海洋CMS又名SEACMS，完全开源免费，自适应电脑、手机、平板、APP多终端，无加密、更安全，是您最佳的建站工具!
爬滚打多年，海洋CMS有着丰富的经验和技术积累，并且能够随着流行趋势加入更多当下流行的功能。
location / { rewrite ^/frim/index(.+?)\.html$ /list/index.php?$1 last; rewrite ^/movie/index(.+?)\.html$ /detail/index.php?$1 last; rewrite ^/play/([0-9]+)-([0-9]+)-([0-9]+)\.html$ /video/index.php?$1-$2-$3 last; rewrite ^/topic/index(.+?)\.html$ /topic/index.php?$1 last; rewrite ^/index.php(.*)$ /index.php?s=$1 last; rewrite ^/(.*)$ /index.php?s=$1 last; rewrite ^/topiclist/index(.+?).html$ /topiclist/index.php?$1 last; rewrite ^/index\.html$ index.php permanent; rewrite ^/news\.html$ news/ permanent; rewrite ^/part/index(.+?)\.html$ /articlelist/index.php?$1 last; rewrite ^/article/index(.+?)\.html$ /article/index.php?$1 last; }
